| Path | Platform | Language |
|------|----------|----------|
| `android/app/src/main/java/com/clavi/keyboard/` | Android IME | Kotlin |
| `ios/ClaviKeyboard/ClaviKeyboardExtension/` | iOS Keyboard | Swift |
